<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1561654-is-firozsha-baag-a-real-building-in-mumbai">Is Firozsha Baag a real building in Mumbai or a fictional one? 
I&#39;m currently reading &quot;A Fine Balance&quot; and it mentioned Firozsha Baag, but &quot;Tales from Firozsha Baag&quot; is publish 12 years after the times in which AFB was set in (1975). So I&#39;m somewhat confused.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1561654'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F828698.Tales_from_Firozsha_Baag">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1561654-is-firozsha-baag-a-real-building-in-mumbai">2 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1561654-is-firozsha-baag-a-real-building-in-mumbai">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

