<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/101926129-madhav"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1590939682i/101926129._UY100_CR25,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/101926129-madhav">Madhav </a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Hi, just came across this question. Whilst the book was written in 1987, the stories are set much earlier - in the 1960s and 70s. Hence Firozsha Bagh <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Hi, just came across this question. Whilst the book was written in 1987, the stories are set much earlier - in the 1960s and 70s. Hence Firozsha Bagh would've "existed" in 1975 i.e. the time at which A Fine Balance is set. :-)<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
