      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/814396-tales-from-firozsha-baag">Quotes from Swimming Lessons ...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;World can be a bewildering place,and dreams and ambitions are often paths to the most pernicious of traps&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/463713-world-can-be-a-bewildering-place-and-dreams-and-ambitions-are">19 likes</a>
            </nobr>
            <div class="clear"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Don't you see, said Father, that you are confusing fiction with facts, fiction does not create facts, fiction can come from facts, it can grow out of facts by compounding, transposing, augmenting, diminishing, or altering them in any way; but you must not confuse cause and effect, you must not confuse what really happened with what the story says happened, you must not lose your grasp on reality, that way madness lies.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/796152-don-t-you-see-said-father-that-you-are-confusing-fiction">6 likes</a>
            </nobr>
            <div class="clear"></div>
          </div>
